About me

I graduated Milwaukee Institute of Art & Design, Majoring in Industrial Design and Minoring in Communicaition Design. After graduating I worked for General Motors, as a contractor, for 3 years. After leaving General Motors, I moved back to Illinois to pursue other career opportunities. I am pursuing a career shift, from physical product design to digital product design, UX/UI.
